text:
Check out this story on jacksonsun.com: http://usat.ly/1RRaKun A story from a long time ago in a galaxy far, far away is only a couple months away from a theater near you. The final trailer for Star Wars: The Force Awakens will debut during halftime of ESPN's Monday Night Football .
 The Jackson Sun.
